                                "byte_start": 91023,
                                "byte_stop": 127699,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 92-896, Thunder Basin Coal Company against Reich will be announced by Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.145,
                        "stop": 107.807,
